        <Sticky classid="Sticky" id="1885750198" x="900" y="540" w="396" h="414" colors="0, 15792890" layer="">
          <paramlist>
            <param name="font" value="2" />
            <param name="align" value="0" />
            <param name="style" value="1" />
            <param name="fg_color" value="0" />
            <param name="bg_color" value="16777215" />
            <param name="arrows" value="0" />
            <param name="full_font" value="Tahoma, 14.25pt" />
            <param name="opacity" value="25" />
            <param name="fg_color_adv" value="#FF000000" />
            <param name="bg_color_adv" value="#FFFFFFFF" />
            <param name="hl_color_adv" value="#FFFFFF00" />
          </paramlist><![CDATA[Grid side converter & controls:
The grid side converter is in charge of controlling the DC link voltage and reactive power.The reactive power control in this converter is normally set to inject zero Q 

The inputs to the controller are:
- The current and voltage of converter terminal (Iconv and V_GS) measured at the terminal of converter 
- The dc link voltage Ecap 
- The reactive power (Q_GS) at the terminal of converter 
- The enabling signal (DBlk_Gr) dictates the time when the controllers starts ]]></Sticky>
        <Sticky classid="Sticky" id="483028172" x="2754" y="468" w="396" h="306" colors="0, 15792890" layer="">
          <paramlist>
            <param name="font" value="2" />
            <param name="align" value="0" />
            <param name="style" value="1" />
            <param name="fg_color" value="0" />
            <param name="bg_color" value="16777215" />
            <param name="arrows" value="4" />
            <param name="full_font" value="Tahoma, 14.25pt" />
            <param name="opacity" value="25" />
            <param name="fg_color_adv" value="#FF000000" />
            <param name="bg_color_adv" value="#FFFFFFFF" />
            <param name="hl_color_adv" value="#FFFFFF00" />
          </paramlist><![CDATA[Rotor side converter & controls:
This converter is in charge of controlling active and reactive power.
 
The inputs of the controller are:
- The current and voltage of rotor (I_RS and V_RS) measured at the terminal of converter 
- The dc link voltage Ecap 
- The enabling signal (DBlk_CrowRtr) that dictates the time when the controllers start operating 

]]></Sticky>
        <Sticky classid="Sticky" id="810162821" x="1836" y="756" w="360" h="90" colors="0, 15792890" layer="">
          <paramlist>
            <param name="font" value="2" />
            <param name="align" value="0" />
            <param name="style" value="1" />
            <param name="fg_color" value="0" />
            <param name="bg_color" value="16777215" />
            <param name="arrows" value="0" />
