            <param name="bg_color_adv" value="#FFFFFFFF" />
            <param name="hl_color_adv" value="#FFFFFF00" />
          </paramlist><![CDATA[If the dc link voltage (Ecap) reaches to a certain limit (Vdc_chop_on) the coper will activated to reduce the voltage level

]]></Sticky>
